summary: This is an email chain forwarding a revised premises search warrant bundle for the Southern District of New York (SDNY), likely related to the Epstein investigation. It includes an attached affidavit and warrant, indicating ongoing legal proceedings.

events.title: Forwarding of Revised SDNY Search Warrant Bundle
events.description: An email chain forwards a second revised copy of the SDNY premises search warrant bundle, including a signed affidavit and warrant.

keyFacts: A second revised premises search warrant bundle for SDNY was circulated via email on July 2, 2020.
The email includes an attached signed affidavit and warrant.
The document indicates ongoing legal activity, likely related to the Epstein case, in mid-2020.
